returns._0: True if all votes are cast; false otherwise.

castVotes(address,uint256,uint256,uint25.details: This function is restricted to being called by the GovernanceProxy only. It first calculates the highest cluster of votes needed and saves the voting state. Then it proceeds to the next stage of the voting process with any remaining votes.

params.abstainVotes: The total votes abstaining from the proposal.
params.againstVotes: The total votes against the proposal.
params.forVotes: The total votes in favor of the proposal.
params.governor: The Governor contract managing the proposal.
params.proposalId: The unique identifier of the proposal.

continueCastingVotes(address,uint256).details: This function resumes the voting process started by `castVotes`, iterating over clusters to allocate votes.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

params.calldatas: Array of calldata for the proposal actions.
params.governor: The governor contract that manages the proposal.
params.targets: Array of target addresses for the proposal.
params.values: Array of values for the proposal actions.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setClusterRegistry(address).details: Restricted to only the owner. Throws an error if clusterRegistry is already set.

params._clusterRegistry: The new cluster registry contract address

setGovernanceProxy(address).details: Restricted to only the owner. Throws an error if governanceProxy is already set.

params._governanceProxy: The new governance proxy contract address

setLiquidityManager(address).details: Restricted to only the owner. Throws an error if liquidityManager is already set.

params._liquidityManager: The new liquidity manager contract address

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

continueCastingVotes(address,uint256).notice: Continues casting votes for a specific proposal and governor.
